  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The mageknight may spend a spell point as a swift action to increase her damage dealt to creatures depending on how many times she has hit them. For 1 round per level, whenever she successfully strikes an opponent with a weapon or natural attack, she gains a cumulative +1 bonus on future damage rolls, to a maximum equal to her class level. If she misses with an attack, the bonus to damage decreases by 1 (minimum 0).</p>\n",
